                                 Gen IX. Vers. 23. 
                              so that their faces were turned backwards and they saw not his shame. O thou wonderfull God! How very Mystically and Secretly dost thou carry thy works: who would know and understand thy wayes if thy spirit did not lead us, and open the understanding.

